1. Deprecate course_data.dart (Optional)
Purpose: Stop using hardcoded data and switch to API calls.
Action:

Keep the file as reference (or delete if unused).

Remove all references to CourseData.getCourses() and CourseData.getPlatforms() from your UI code.


2. Update Navigation
Wherever you previously used the hardcoded list:

// Old navigation (using static data)
Navigator.push(
  context,
  MaterialPageRoute(builder: (context) => OldCourseListScreen()),
);

// New navigation (using dynamic search)
Navigator.push(
  context,
  MaterialPageRoute(builder: (context) => CourseSearchScreen()),
);

3.Android Permissions
Add internet access to android/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />

4 Error handling (optional): if everything done, can look into it.

